data.description: Come watch the sunset from the large back deck, with a view of the neighboring farm fields. This beautiful property in Misty Meadows has one of the largest back yards in the development! You will have plenty of room in this 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home with a first floor den and a poured basement ready to be finished. The gorgeous island is a great place to entertain while in the kitchen. Two of the bedrooms have walk-in closets and the large master bedroom and bath just got new flooring.  The laundry room is conveniently located near the bedrooms on the second floor. There will be new flooring in master bed/bath. You will feel like you are in the country, while being close to stores, restaurants and Rte 33 for easy access to C-bus. New roof and flooring! Invisible fence! Motivated Seller!
